name: ConditionalFormatPercentValueRule
description: Represents a percentage-based (top or bottom) conditional format.

properties.name: percent
properties.description: Represents the value percentage to apply this conditional format to.

properties.name: direction
properties.description: Represents "top" or "bottom", the section to apply this conditional format to.

methods.name: load
methods.description: Fills the proxy object created in JavaScript layer with property and object values specified in the parameter.

parameters.name: param
parameters.description: Accepts parameter and relationship names as delimited string or an array. Or, provide [loadOption](loadoption.md) object.
